1
00:00:00,540 --> 00:00:05,260
Yuki-kun! Long time no see.

2
00:00:06,210 --> 00:00:07,340
Yeah.

3
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:09,970
You've been ditching us lately.
You doing okay?

4
00:00:09,970 --> 00:00:10,970
I'm fine.

5
00:00:10,970 --> 00:00:13,760
Don't you think it's about time
you joined our mixer with the N High girls?

6
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:15,390
You guys will be fine without me.

7
00:00:15,390 --> 00:00:19,390
The girls won't show up if you're not there.
Right?

8
00:00:21,270 --> 00:00:24,230
Well... I guess we could take this guy instead.

9
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:27,900
Hey! You've never been to a mixer, have you?

10
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:30,070
Hey!
We'll put you to good use.

11
00:00:30,070 --> 00:00:31,570
Cut it out.

12
00:00:31,570 --> 00:00:35,370
You can come along too, right?

13
00:00:36,160 --> 00:00:37,700
Makoto, let's go.

14
00:00:39,620 --> 00:00:42,790
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
You're not going anywhere. Heh.

15
00:00:43,420 --> 00:00:48,340
Oh, right!
I heard you two are aiming for the "Prince Pageant" at the festival?

16
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:54,760
I mean, you've improved a little...

17
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:57,600
But that's way out of your league.

18
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,150
Don't touch him.

19
00:01:03,150 --> 00:01:05,520
Whoa. Don't get so full of yourself.

20
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:07,650
Whoa! Ooh!

21
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,820
- Quit joking around!
- What's with the attitude?

22
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:12,410
Stop it, you idiot! Yuki!

23
00:01:12,410 --> 00:01:14,700
Yuki! Stop! Yuki!

24
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:17,120
Yuki, control yourself! Don't fight!

25
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,660
Yuki, stop it! Stop right now!

26
00:01:18,660 --> 00:01:20,080
Stop it, Yuki!
